Beta 1997 release of Inferno 1.0 Build 1 from Lucent's Inferno Business Unit.

This software was originally provided by Lucent Technologies Inc under NOTICE.orig and LICENSE.orig.
It is now being made available under the new licence in NOTICE, by Vita Nuova Holdings Limited,
under an agreement with Lucent on 1 March 2000.

With the exception of new NOTICE files and this README, it is provided here as originally distributed,
for historical reference.

* there is no non-Limbo source (they didn't include it)
* there is no Plan 9 support
* there is a `Distributed Sports Program' demo (with source and images)
